We do not yet know exactly how this money will be used, but we wanted to take this opportunity to thank once again all our supporters who made this funding possible.

Thanks also to *Jehan* from [LILA](https://libreart.info/en/), who accepted to manage the reception of the donations for \G'MIC. Also a special thanks to *Sam* from [FOSSHUB](https://www.fosshub.com/) who is a reccuring donor and who also offers an efficient hosting service for our files to download.

